Implement the function f that takes n as a parametre,
and returns a vector of size n, such that the value of the element at index i is the fatcorial of i if i is veen
or the sum of unmbers from 1 to i toherwise.
i starts from 1.
the factorial of i is the multiplication of the numebrs from 1 to i (1 * 2 * ... * i).
